&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage daily business operations and issue resolution and performance tracking for existing DCB and LPM partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a payment expertise and provide guidance on DCB and LPM-related requests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and grow relationships with existing merchants, business and payment partners to drive transaction volume and performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and research new business opportunities, key contacts, and decision-makers of new payment partners (carriers, wallets, fintech platforms) and local merchants who want to global market across Taiwan, Hong Kong, and China.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Negotiate best commercials offers/cost and performance optimizations with carriers, eWallets, banks, and payment providers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support new merchant launches in the region by aligning with product, integration, compliance, and legal teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with Partner Relationship Network (PRM), Customer Success, Tech, BI, Product, Finance, Risk, Compliance, and Operations teams for optimization plans to improve payment flows, API integrations, settlement, and user experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor regulatory updates, market trends, and competitor activities in the payments industry.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help optimize internal and external processes to improve efficiency and business results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and deliver impactful business proposals, presentations, and partner reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Measures of Success&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improved DCB and LPM partner performance, including transaction success rates, service quality, and overall payment reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
